Your Highness.

13
00:01:43,160 --> 00:01:44,080
Greetings, sir.

14
00:01:46,240 --> 00:01:48,560
Under your leadership, Capital Security has

15
00:01:48,560 --> 00:01:51,080
solved difficult cases and upheld justice.

16
00:01:51,720 --> 00:01:53,800
You're one of a kind,

17
00:01:54,360 --> 00:01:56,120
with unmatched talent.

18
00:01:57,520 --> 00:01:58,920
That's very nice of you to say.

19
00:01:59,800 --> 00:02:00,840
With all due respect,

20
00:02:01,160 --> 00:02:02,880
I can't let Si

21
00:02:03,720 --> 00:02:05,200
marry you.

22
00:02:09,640 --> 00:02:10,480
Sir,

23
00:02:11,720 --> 00:02:12,680
did I do

24
00:02:12,680 --> 00:02:13,880
anything wrong?

25
00:02:13,880 --> 00:02:15,000
Please enlighten me.

26
00:02:17,320 --> 00:02:18,320
Your Highness,

27
00:02:19,160 --> 00:02:20,600
you're a prince.

28
00:02:21,360 --> 00:02:22,920
Ever since you were born,

29
00:02:23,440 --> 00:02:24,920
you've been involved

30
00:02:24,920 --> 00:02:26,440
in power struggle.

31
00:02:26,920 --> 00:02:29,240
If Si married you,

32
00:02:29,760 --> 00:02:33,480
