33
00:02:38,800 --> 00:02:39,640
Sir,

34
00:02:40,800 --> 00:02:42,720
I promise to do my utmost

35
00:02:42,960 --> 00:02:44,280
to protect her

36
00:02:45,360 --> 00:02:47,760
and lead a peaceful life with her.

37
00:02:49,480 --> 00:02:50,640
I fear

38
00:02:52,120 --> 00:02:54,000
it'll turn out the opposite.

39
00:02:55,600 --> 00:02:57,720
You won't have a choice.

40
00:03:01,420 --> 00:03:04,420
(Haitang Chamber)

41
00:03:04,600 --> 00:03:06,800
(Qi)
Do you truly like Prince Yan?

42
00:03:15,360 --> 00:03:16,440
I admire him.

43
00:03:21,520 --> 00:03:23,160
I hate to upset you,

44
00:03:23,560 --> 00:03:25,080
but I've been in love, too.

45
00:03:25,480 --> 00:03:26,800
Here's my advice.

46
00:03:27,760 --> 00:03:28,800
As a prince

47
00:03:29,200 --> 00:03:30,240
of the imperial family,

48
00:03:30,960 --> 00:03:32,040
even if you two managed to

49
00:03:32,040 --> 00:03:33,030
hurdle the first barrier,

50
00:03:33,120 --> 00:03:34,590
and you were married into his mansion,

51
00:03:34,920 --> 00:03:36,720
no one could guarantee you'd live

52
00:03:36,840 --> 00:03:37,680
happily ever after.

53
00:03:38,680 --> 00:03:39,640
Don't worry about me.

54
00:03:39,960 --> 00:03:41,200
I'll take good care of myself.

55
00:03:44,180 --> 00:03:45,260
(Qi)

56
00:03:45,280 --> 00:03:46,120
Look at it.

57
00:04:01,480 --> 00:04:04,880
I'm simply curious.

58
00:04:06,640 --> 00:04:08,160
Why do you

59
00:04:08,160 --> 00:04:09,640
desire to be a heroine?

60
00:04:12,120 --> 00:04:13,280
I grew up in the army.

61
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:15,200
I was surrounded by men.

62
00:04:16,600 --> 00:04:18,240
I heard all kinds of stories

63
00:04:18,240 --> 00:04:19,440
of heroes in my childhood.

64
00:04:20,160 --> 00:04:21,800
They made me wonder

65
00:04:22,600 --> 00:04:23,480
why the heroes

66
00:04:23,480 --> 00:04:24,800
in those stories

67
00:04:24,800 --> 00:04:25,920
were always men

68
00:04:26,720 --> 00:04:27,560
while women

69
00:04:27,840 --> 00:04:29,320
could only wait for their help.

70
00:04:30,080 --> 00:04:30,920
I found that unfair.

71
00:04:32,160 --> 00:04:33,240
Who says

72
00:04:33,720 --> 00:04:35,080
women can't be heroes?

73
00:04:36,040 --> 00:04:36,880
If men can be heroes,

74
00:04:38,400 --> 00:04:39,840
so can I, Lu Chuchu.

75
00:04:42,120 --> 00:04:43,560
I see.

76
00:04:47,380 --> 00:04:49,280
You're quite special.

77
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:50,760
It seems

78
00:04:52,040 --> 00:04:53,020
that nothing can stop you

79
00:04:53,020 --> 00:04:54,120
from doing what you want.

80
00:04:54,920 --> 00:04:56,000
You only follow your heart.

81
00:05:01,560 --> 00:05:02,400
Jiang Zhan,

82
00:05:04,280 --> 00:05:05,360
