83
00:05:21,240 --> 00:05:22,160
My sister is the same.

84
00:05:23,960 --> 00:05:25,800
Both of you have big hearts.

85
00:05:29,840 --> 00:05:30,720
It should be

86
00:05:31,000 --> 00:05:32,240
these people.

87
00:05:33,360 --> 00:05:34,680
The eclipse had been

88
00:05:34,680 --> 00:05:36,520
predicted and recorded.

89
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:37,840
Read this.

90
00:05:39,920 --> 00:05:42,280
It says the next day,

91
00:05:42,680 --> 00:05:44,160
they overturned

92
00:05:44,160 --> 00:05:45,320
all the previous predictions.

93
00:05:47,960 --> 00:05:49,840
No wonder Supervisor Yang Nianzhi

94
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:52,360
didn't receive any predictions
of the eclipse.

95
00:05:52,360 --> 00:05:54,520
Thankfully, we found
the Nightingale's secret letters.

96
00:05:55,040 --> 00:05:57,040
Otherwise, even if the eclipse were true,

97
00:05:57,160 --> 00:05:58,720
they'd be guilty of negligence at most.

98
00:05:59,000 --> 00:05:59,840
We can't wait.

99
00:06:00,080 --> 00:06:01,440
I'll put together the evidence

100
00:06:01,440 --> 00:06:02,560
and present it to His Majesty

101
